id: jf-8oz6
title: Make four-metric coverage portable across Bun and Node
description: "Add a typed Node test-runtime adapter for the Bun.spawn and Bun.serve harness boundaries, keep live read-only E2E separate, expose deterministic Vitest execution and four-dimensional coverage diagnostics, and make portable execution part of release validation."
type: Task
status: closed
priority: 0
tags[7]: agents,bun,coverage,node,release-gate,testing,vitest
created_at: "2026-07-22T04:51:32.380Z"
updated_at: "2026-07-22T04:58:08.822Z"
closed_at: "2026-07-22T04:58:07.635Z"
author: codex-jellyfin
estimated_minutes: 120
acceptance_criteria: All deterministic non-live tests pass under Vitest without changing production runtime behavior; Vitest reports statements branches functions and lines across every source file including src/cli.ts; The compiled jf-cli live read-only suite remains a separate passing gate; Release validation includes the cross-runtime suite and documentation records honest non-100 coverage
definition_of_ready: Exact Bun-only failure surface measured; no matching all-status pm child exists; live instance configuration remains private and read-only.
goal: jf-mqpo
value: Creates the trustworthy measurement boundary required to finish the governed 100 percent coverage goal.
impact: Removes 254 Node-runtime harness failures and prevents Bun-only tests from hiding missing branch and statement coverage.
outcome: One deterministic four-metric diagnostic plus independent Bun and live E2E proof.
why_now: The 100 percent release blocker cannot be addressed honestly until all four dimensions are measurable.
parent: jf-mkzh
reviewer: github-bots
risk: medium
confidence: high
resolution: "Added a typed Node compatibility adapter for Bun test harness APIs, separated live E2E from attributable coverage, added portable/four-metric scripts, and required the portable suite in release validation."
expected_result: "All deterministic tests run under Vitest, four dimensions are measurable, live E2E remains independent, and release validation stays green."
actual_result: "894/894 Vitest tests, 177/177 live compiled CLI E2E tests, and the complete release gate pass; exact four-metric baseline is documented without claiming 100 percent."
