comments[2]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-22T04:51:32.380Z",codex-jellyfin,Implementation completed after reproducing 254 Vitest failures caused only by missing Bun.spawn and Bun.serve globals; focused and full portable suites now pass.
  "2026-07-22T04:58:06.379Z",codex-jellyfin,"Direct linked commands all pass, but pm test --run is blocked before command execution by upstream core bug https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/issues/642. Verified results are retained from direct runs; this completed jellyfin-cli task is not blocked by the tracker-runner defect."
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-22T04:51:32.380Z",codex-jellyfin,Coverage is intentionally documented as 38.19/37.40/49.92/37.87 rather than represented as complete.
learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-22T04:51:32.380Z",codex-jellyfin,Black-box child-process E2E and attributable in-process coverage are complementary gates; neither should be substituted for the other.
